'''2014-15年也门政变'''从2014年末开始持续到2015年1月，意在迫使也门政府下台<ref name="iranian">{{cite news|url=http://www.ibtimes.com/yemen-coup-sign-expanding-iranian-influence-middle-east-1790420#.VMGjHKP1_WA.twitter|agency=International Business Times|title=Yemen 'Coup' A Sign Of Expanding Iranian Influence In the Middle East|date=22 January 2015|accessdate=22 January 2015|archive-date=2020-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124134908/https://www.ibtimes.com/yemen-coup-sign-expanding-iranian-influence-middle-east-1790420#.VMGjHKP1_WA.twitter|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2015/01/22/the-next-king-of-the-saudis-salman-the-family-sheriff.html?via=twitter_page|agency=The Daily Beast|title=The Next King Of The Saudis: Salman, The Family Sheriff|first=Bruce|last=Riedel|date=22 January 2015|accessdate=22 January 2015|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304132740/http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2015/01/22/the-next-king-of-the-saudis-salman-the-family-sheriff.html?via=twitter_page|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2015/01/20/world/yemen-violence/|agency=CNN|title=Yemen's President 'has no control' as Houthi rebels storm palace|date=20 January 2015|accessdate=22 January 2015|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108114409/https://edition.cnn.com/2015/01/20/world/yemen-violence/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.msnbc.com/msnbc/us-war-terror-threatened-yemen-coup|agency=MSNBC|title=US war on terror threatened by Yemen coup|date=23 January 2015|accessdate=23 January 2015|archive-date=2020-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200505010738/http://www.msnbc.com/msnbc/us-war-terror-threatened-yemen-coup|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[胡塞武装组织|胡塞叛军]]在2014年9月21日进入首都[[萨那|萨那]]开始政变，总理[[穆罕默德·萨利姆·巴桑杜|穆罕默德·萨利姆·巴桑杜]]因此辞职。2015年1月22日在胡塞军占领总统府、官邸和重要军事设施后，总统[[阿卜杜·拉布·曼苏尔·哈迪|阿卜杜·拉布·曼苏尔·哈迪]]及其内阁辞职。

也门的政治局势在2014年恶化。一系列的静坐和示威游行演变成持续到2015年的武装冲突。2014年8月18日胡塞在萨那发动了一系列针对油价上涨的示威活动。9月21日胡塞军控制萨那并迫使总理巴桑杜辞职，胡赛组织之后与其他政党签署协议成立了新的统一政府。除了胡塞和政府的冲突外，其和[[基地组织阿拉伯半岛分支|基地组织阿拉伯半岛分支]]间的冲突也体现在了这一系列的抗议中。

2015年1月20日胡塞军出乎意料地攻占总统府，而且包围并炮轰总统哈迪的私人官邸。正在官邸工作的哈迪没有受伤，但胡塞军夺取了首都的更多地区且有效地控制了也门政府<ref name="shell">{{cite news|title=Rebels capture Yemen presidential palace, shell residence|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/world/2015/01/20/yemen-shiite-rebels/22038397/|accessdate=20 January 2015|date=20 January 2015|newspaper=USA today|archive-date=2020-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107053818/https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/world/2015/01/20/yemen-shiite-rebels/22038397/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="takeover"/>。1月21日亚丁最高安全委员会关闭所有通往亚丁省的海陆空入口<ref>{{cite web|last1=Al-Khameri|first1=Bassam|script-title=en:Aden shuts all entry points over Sana’a “coup”|url=http://www.yementimes.com/en/1853/news/4821/Aden-shuts-all-entry-points-over-Sana’a-“coup”.htm|website=www.yementimes.com|publisher=Yemen Times|accessdate=23 January 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170407045353/http://www.yementimes.com/en/1853/news/4821/Aden-shuts-all-entry-points-over-Sana%E2%80%99a-%E2%80%9Ccoup%E2%80%9D.htm|archive-date=2017-04-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。1月22日哈迪内阁集体辞职。当天新闻部长纳迪亚·阿萨卡夫（Nadia Al-Sakkaf）表示，议会否决了总统的辞职请求。根据也门宪法，哈迪的权力理论上将持续至2015年4月22日<ref>{{cite web|last1=Mohsen|first1=Ahlam|title=Cabinet and Hadi resign|url=http://www.yementimes.com/en/1853/news/4830/Cabinet-and-Hadi-resign.htm|website=www.yementimes.com|publisher=Yemen Times|accessdate=23 January 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150421001911/http://www.yementimes.com/en/1853/news/4830/Cabinet-and-Hadi-resign.htm|archive-date=2015-04-21|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

== 背景 ==
{{Main|也门什叶派起义}}

胡塞军起初于2014年8月18日进驻首都萨那，设立抗议大本营<ref name="BBCGardner"/>。数万名人士参与抗议，随之将其演变成冲突。9月10日有7名示威者被安全部队开枪射杀，9月18日再度爆发的冲突导致40名示威者和逊尼派民兵死亡<ref name="BBCGardner"/>。

抗议活动伴随着胡塞的扩张，于2014年7月8日在胡塞军占领的省会[[阿姆兰|阿姆兰]]达到高潮<ref>{{cite news|title=Military shake-up in Amran|url=http://www.yementimes.com/en/1798/news/4094/Military-shake-up-in-Amran.htm|author=Ali Saeed|accessdate=29 October 2014|date=15 July 2014|newspaper=Yemen Times|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151221005802/http://www.yementimes.com/en/1798/news/4094/Military-shake-up-in-Amran.htm|archive-date=2015-12-21|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。军队击败了310装甲旅，击毙指挥官[[哈密德·奎沙比|哈密德·奎沙比]]（Hameed Al-Qushaibi）<ref>{{cite news|title=Houthis hand over Al-Qushaibi's corpse to the state|url=http://www.yementimes.com/en/1800/news/4118/Houthis-hand-over-Al-Qushaibi%E2%80%99s-corpse-to-the-state.htm|date=22 July 2014|accessdate=29 October 2014|author=Ali Ibrahim Al-Moshki|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150123152222/http://www.yementimes.com/en/1800/news/4118/Houthis-hand-over-Al-Qushaibi%E2%80%99s-corpse-to-the-state.htm|archive-date=2015-01-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Fall of Amran sends shock waves across Yemen|url=http://www.al-monitor.com/pulse/originals/2014/07/fall-of-amran-yemen-and-the-repercussions.html#|date=July 2014|accessdate=29 October 2014|newspaper=Al-Monitor|author=Maysa Shujah Al-Deen|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141018194432/http://www.al-monitor.com/pulse/originals/2014/07/fall-of-amran-yemen-and-the-repercussions.html|archivedate=2014年10月18日|df=}}</ref>。

然而因油价接近完全上涨而随即触发的抗议，让也门政府于7月29日决定削减燃油补贴<ref name="BBCGardner">{{cite news|title=Frank Gardner: Yemen at risk of civil war, says ambassador|author=Frank Gardner|publisher=BBC|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-29749046|accessdate=29 October 2014|date=24 October 2014|archive-date=2020-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200505010756/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-29749046|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年燃油补贴成本让也门政府花费30亿，是国家预算的近33%<ref name="ReutersGobari">{{cite news|title=Tens of thousands of Yemeni Houthis protest against govt in capital|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/08/22/us-yemen-protests-idUSKBN0GM12C20140822|date=22 August 2014|accessdate=29 October 2014|newspaper=Reuters|author=Mohammed Ghobari|archive-date=2015-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151127125233/http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/08/22/us-yemen-protests-idUSKBN0GM12C20140822|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。为回应削减，胡塞军就恢复补贴和组建新政府发动抗议<ref>{{cite web|title=What Do the Protesting Houthis Really Want in Yemen?|author=Peter Salisbury|url=https://news.vice.com/article/what-do-the-protesting-houthis-really-want-in-yemen|accessdate=29 October 2014|date=11 September 2014|publisher=Vice|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150927193720/https://news.vice.com/article/what-do-the-protesting-houthis-really-want-in-yemen|archive-date=2015-09-27|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

== 事件 ==
=== 2014年：胡塞军控制萨那 ===
9月19日，叛军袭击萨那，9月21日提前进入城市攻占政府总部，致使指责军队和政府支持起义，谴责哈迪的[[也门总理|总理]][[穆罕默德·萨利姆·巴桑杜|穆罕默德·萨利姆·巴桑杜]]辞职<ref name="ae">{{cite news|url=http://www.thenational.ae/world/middle-east/yemeni-prime-minister-resigns-as-shiite-rebels-sieze-government-headquarters|agency=The National|title=Yemeni prime minister resigns as Shiite rebels sieze government headquarters|date=21 September 2014|accessdate=22 January 2015|archive-date=2016-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160421075049/http://www.thenational.ae/world/middle-east/yemeni-prime-minister-resigns-as-shiite-rebels-sieze-government-headquarters|dead-url=no}}</ref>。胡塞军连同也门其他政治团体，签署题为《和平合作协定》的协议，组建新的统一政府<ref name="Aawsat">{{cite news|title=Houthis secure six ministerial portfolios in new Yemeni cabinet|url=http://www.aawsat.net/2014/10/article55337905|date=26 October 2014|accessdate=29 October 2014|newspaper=ASharq Al-Awsat|author=Hamdan Al-Rahbi|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141029134357/http://www.aawsat.net/2014/10/article55337905|archivedate=2014年10月29日}}</ref>。

9月22日，萨那的战斗至少造成340人死亡<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://dailystar.com.lb/News/Middle-East/2014/Sep-22/271549-at-least-200-killed-in-recent-yemen-fighting-ministry.ashx#axzz3E3iuXhsm |title=Daily Star - Yemen fighting killed at least 200 within week: govt |accessdate=2015-01-24 |archive-date=2016-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309063031/http://dailystar.com.lb/News/Middle-East/2014/Sep-22/271549-at-least-200-killed-in-recent-yemen-fighting-ministry.ashx#axzz3E3iuXhsm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。战斗在权力分享协会签订后仍在继续<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Middle-East/2014/Sep-27/272202-houthi-rebels-attack-yemen-security-chiefs-home.ashx#axzz3DwXZNAOv |title=Daily Star - Houthi rebels attack Yemen security chief's home |accessdate=2015-01-24 |archive-date=2015-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150929101332/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Middle-East/2014/Sep-27/272202-houthi-rebels-attack-yemen-security-chiefs-home.ashx#axzz3DwXZNAOv |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

总统阿卜杜·拉布·曼苏尔·哈迪的办公室主任[[艾哈迈德·阿瓦德·本·穆巴拉克|艾哈迈德·阿瓦德·本·穆巴拉克]]，最初于10月7日被提名为巴桑杜的继任者，但他在胡塞军的施压下拒绝该职务<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/10/08/us-yemen-security-idUSKCN0HX28P20141008|agency=Reuters|title=Yemen's new prime minister quits after Houthis call mass protest|date=8 October 2014|accessdate=22 January 2015|archive-date=2015-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150927121620/http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/10/08/us-yemen-security-idUSKCN0HX28P20141008|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。双方123名战士在战斗中被击毙<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2014/09/yemen-houthi-rebels-advance-into-sanaa-201492091233845119.html |title=Al-Jazeera - Yemen's Houthi rebels advance into Sanaa |accessdate=2015-01-24 |archive-date=2015-09-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150911222918/http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2014/09/yemen-houthi-rebels-advance-into-sanaa-201492091233845119.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

10月9日，[[解放广场|解放广场]]一枚自杀式炸弹破坏了原定举行的大型集会。袭击造成47人丧生，75人受伤，绝大多数是胡塞军的支持者。政府官员认为袭击由[[基地组织阿拉伯半岛分支|基地组织阿拉伯半岛分支]]策划，该组织跟胡塞军和也门政府存在过节<ref>{{cite news|last1=Salisbury|first1=Peter|title=Yemen suicide attack kills dozens|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/oct/09/yemen-suicide-attack-kills-20|accessdate=9 October 2014|agency=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|date=9 October 2014|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112015606/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/oct/09/yemen-suicide-attack-kills-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

10月13日，哈迪跟胡塞军达成协议，任命[[哈立德·巴哈|哈立德·巴哈]]为总理，填补上月巴桑杜受压力辞职所留下的空缺职位<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2014/10/new-yemeni-prime-minister-appointed-20141013112111586298.html|agency=Al Jazeera|title=Yemen appoints new PM to end crisis|date=13 October 2014|accessdate=22 January 2015|archive-date=2019-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190409214606/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2014/10/new-yemeni-prime-minister-appointed-20141013112111586298.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

11月7日，[[联合国安理会|联合国安理会]]制裁阻扰也门政治进程的前总统[[阿里·阿卜杜拉·萨利赫|阿里·阿卜杜拉·萨利赫]]，以及胡塞军两名指挥官阿卜杜拉·叶海亚·哈基姆和阿卜杜勒·哈利克·胡锡<ref>{{cite news|title=U.N. sanctions Yemen's ex-President Saleh, two rebel leaders|url=http://uk.reuters.com/article/2014/11/07/uk-yemen-un-sanctions-idUKKBN0IR2EC20141107|newspaper=Reuters|date=7 November 2014|accessdate=14 November 2014|author=Michelle Nichols|archive-date=2015-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150927102209/http://uk.reuters.com/article/2014/11/07/uk-yemen-un-sanctions-idUKKBN0IR2EC20141107|dead-url=no}}</ref>。萨利赫的政党[[全国人民大会|全国人民大会]]，为此作出回应，剥夺了总统阿卜杜·拉布·曼苏尔·哈迪的党内职务，指责他煽动制裁<ref name="Aljazeera1">{{cite news|title=Yemen swears in new government amid boycott|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2014/11/yemen-swear-new-government-2014118223745207779.html|accessdate=14 November 2014|date=9 November 2014|newspaper=Al Jazeera|archive-date=2014-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141111191802/http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2014/11/yemen-swear-new-government-2014118223745207779.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

11月9日，在《和平合作协定》呼吁下成立的新政府宣誓就职。然而，胡塞军和全国人民大会拒绝加入新政府<ref name="Aljazeera1"/>。

=== 2015年：政治危机 ===
1月18日，胡塞军绑架总统的办公室主任[[艾哈迈德·阿瓦德·本·穆巴拉克|艾哈迈德·阿瓦德·本·穆巴拉克]]，在争议中平息设立新宪法的提议<ref name="kidnap">{{cite news|url=http://www.ibtimes.com/gunmen-kidnap-yemeni-presidents-chief-staff-ahmed-awad-bin-mubarak-2-security-guards-1786646|agency=International Business Times|title=Gunmen Kidnap Yemeni President's Chief Of Staff Ahmed Awad Bin Mubarak, 2 Security Guards|date=17 January 2015|accessdate=22 January 2015|archive-date=2020-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127010343/https://www.ibtimes.com/gunmen-kidnap-yemeni-presidents-chief-staff-ahmed-awad-bin-mubarak-2-security-guards-1786646|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1月19日，胡塞军包围萨那的首相官邸。当天早些时候叛军和总统卫队爆发激烈冲突，至少8人死亡，随后宣布停战。胡塞活动家侯赛因·阿布哈提表示，组织受到“挑衅”，在星期一的战斗中有两处阵地遭袭<ref>{{cite news|title=Yemen crisis: Houthi rebels surround PM's residence|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-30888190|accessdate=20 January 2015|date=19 January 2015|newspaper=BBC|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108131607/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-30888190|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1月20日，胡塞军袭击总统官邸，扫荡总统府。新闻部长纳迪亚·阿萨卡夫表示，身处住宅内的总统哈迪在一个半小时的“猛烈炮轰”下，受到警卫保护，毫发未损。确保哈迪安全撤离住所后，总统卫队投降。据报道，两名警卫在袭击中被打死。叛军在萨那的街道上徘徊，或坐在配有高射炮的卡车里，在首相官邸和整个城市设卡，加强情报总部在内的重要据点的巡逻。联合国安理会呼吁召开针对事态的紧急会议。[[联合国秘书长|联合国秘书长]][[潘基文|潘基文]]表示关切也门的“局势恶化”，督促各方停止敌对行为<ref name="shell"/><ref>{{cite news|title=Yemen rebels overtake presidential palace|url=http://america.aljazeera.com/articles/2015/1/20/yemen-crisis-negotiations.html|accessdate=20 January 2015|date=20 January 2015|newspaper=Al Jazeera|archive-date=2015-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150120232431/http://america.aljazeera.com/articles/2015/1/20/yemen-crisis-negotiations.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。胡塞运动领袖[[阿卜杜勒-马利克·胡塞|阿卜杜勒-马利克·胡塞]]在也门电视台发表长篇讲话，要求哈迪尽快落实胡塞军所需的政治变革<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/01/21/world/middleeast/presidential-residence-in-yemen-is-attacked.html?_r=0|agency=The New York Times|date=20 January 2015|accessdate=20 January 2015|title=Coup Fears Rise in Yemen as Rebels Storm Palace|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108095707/http://www.nytimes.com/2015/01/21/world/middleeast/presidential-residence-in-yemen-is-attacked.html?_r=0|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|publisher=The Yemen Peace Project|url=http://www.yemenpeaceproject.org/blogpost/analysis-commentary/al-huthi-lays-down-the-law/|accessdate=20 January 2015|date=20 January 2015|title=Al-Huthi Lays Down the Law|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150121083847/http://www.yemenpeaceproject.org/blogpost/analysis-commentary/al-huthi-lays-down-the-law/|archivedate=2015年1月21日}}</ref>。次日，胡塞军卫队占领哈迪住所，但胡塞官员表示，总统可以随心所欲自由来往。也门军方消息人士表示，胡塞军还和平占据了哈迪家附近的军事航空学院和萨那的主要导弹基地<ref name="takeover">{{cite news|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2015/01/21/yemen-president-houthi-guard_n_6514692.html|agency=The Huffington Post|title=Yemen's President Under Guard Of Houthi Rebels|date=January 21, 2015|accessdate=January 21, 2015|archive-date=2017-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171012063623/https://www.huffingtonpost.com/2015/01/21/yemen-president-houthi-guard_n_6514692.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

也门南部港市[[亚丁|亚丁]]地方官员鉴于总统府被胡塞军占据，关闭了该市的机场、港口和陆路口岸。市地方安全委员会称胡塞军的举动是“针对总统个人和整个政治进程的侵略性政变<ref name="takeover"/>”。

1月21日，政府军和胡塞军达成停火协议，反政府武装的多项要求得以满足，如在议会和国家机构中增加胡塞组织的代表。作为回报，反政府武装表示将撤出其阵地并释放总统办公室主任。然而，停火不久后被打破。

1月22日，哈迪和总理哈立德·巴哈递交辞呈，表示也门的局势已于2014年9月胡塞军进入首都后改变。巴哈为“避免被拖入无法律依据并无建设性的政策深渊中”而宣布辞职<ref name="letters">{{cite news|url=http://www.foxnews.com/world/2015/01/22/shiite-rebels-remain-deployed-outside-yemeni-presidents-house-despite/|agency=Fox News|title=Yemen's president, cabinet resign amid rebel standoff|date=22 January 2015|accessdate=22 January 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150125064554/http://www.foxnews.com/world/2015/01/22/shiite-rebels-remain-deployed-outside-yemeni-presidents-house-despite/|archive-date=2015-01-25|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。虽然胡塞军高级官员据称对哈迪的辞职表示欢迎，但领导层也发表声明称辞职必须在国家议会批准后才能生效。议会当天拒绝了总统的辞职。根据也门宪法第115条，总统必须等待三个月的时间再向议会递交辞呈，届时议会将不能拒绝让总统辞职。哈迪理论上将保留总统职权至4月22日。

=== 权力真空 ===

在政府高层辞职后，亚丁等南方城市的安全官员宣布，不再服从在萨那的中央政府<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-30936940|agency=BBC|title=Yemen crisis: President resigns as rebels tighten hold|date=January 22, 2015|accessdate=January 22, 2015|archive-date=2015-02-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150219075544/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-30936940|dead-url=no}}</ref>。一些报告表明，[[也门民主人民共和国|南部正寻求独立]]<ref>{{cite news|url=http://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/shiite-rebels-remain-yemen-president-house-28396922|agency=ABC News|title=Yemen's US-Backed President Quits; Country Could Split Apart|date=22 January 2015|accessdate=22 January 2015|archive-date=2015-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150130124713/http://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/shiite-rebels-remain-yemen-president-house-28396922|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1月23日，胡塞军政变后，数千人在[[亚丁|亚丁]]、[[荷台达|荷台达]]、[[伊卜|伊卜]]、[[塔伊茲|塔伊茲]]等城市示威，示威者在[[亚丁国际机场|亚丁国际机场]]和一些政府大楼升起[[也门国旗|南也门国旗]]。一名著名胡塞运动人士从组织辞职，并在Facebook上表示由于胡塞组织已经成为也门当局，他更愿意充当调解员<ref>{{cite news|url=http://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/yemen-rebels-call-protests-day-president-resigns-28425072|agency=ABC News|title=Yemen's Shiite Rebels Try to Avoid Overstepping Amid Protest|date=23 January 2015|accessdate=23 January 2015|archive-date=2015-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150130015100/http://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/yemen-rebels-call-protests-day-president-resigns-28425072|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

据[[路透社|路透社]]报道，1月25日，南部独立运动的几位领导人宣布南部分裂，但没有讲是整个地区<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/01/25/us-yemen-security-fragmentation-analysis-idUSKBN0KY0BR20150125|agency=Reuters|title=Yemen risks disintegration as south rejects Shi'ite group's takeover|date=25 January 2015|accessdate=25 January 2015|archive-date=2015-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151010234942/http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/01/25/us-yemen-security-fragmentation-analysis-idUSKBN0KY0BR20150125|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。此外，议会举行特别会议，议员们商榷接受还是拒绝哈迪被取消的辞职。胡塞民兵据报道破坏[[萨那大学|萨那大学]]附近的抗议，该过程中几名记者遭到殴打和拘留<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/wires/afp/article-2925320/Yemen-parliament-postpones-meeting-president-resignation.html|agency=Daily Mail|title=Yemen crisis deepens but Obama vows Qaeda pursuit|date=25 January 2015|accessdate=25 January 2015|archive-date=2020-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200505011006/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/wires/afp/article-2925320/Yemen-parliament-postpones-meeting-president-resignation.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

据报道，有组织代表表示，[[本·穆巴拉克|本·穆巴拉克]]1月27日被胡塞军释放后，移交给[[舍卜沃省|舍卜沃省]]当地部落<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2015/01/houthis-free-top-aide-yemen-president-150127144552184.html|agency=Al Jazeera|title=Houthis free top aide to Yemen president|date=27 January 2015|accessdate=27 January 2015|archive-date=2020-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200907122126/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2015/01/houthis-free-top-aide-yemen-president-150127144552184.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同日，胡塞领导人[[阿卜杜勒·马利克·胡塞|阿卜杜勒·马利克·胡塞]]在电视讲话中，呼吁各政治派别和部落领导人之间举行会谈，结束政治上的不确定性<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.wsj.com/articles/militants-in-yemen-free-presidents-top-aide-1422387831|agency=Wall Street Journal|title=Militants in Yemen Free President’s Top Aide|date=27 January 2015|accessdate=28 January 2015|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108134500/https://www.wsj.com/articles/militants-in-yemen-free-presidents-top-aide-1422387831|dead-url=no}}</ref>。多数派别抵制这次会议，只有[[阿里·阿卜杜拉·萨利赫|阿里·阿卜杜拉·萨利赫]]的[[全国人民大会_(也门)|全国人民大会]]参与讨论。据报道，胡塞军提出由北方和南方等量代表组成的六人“过渡总统委员会”，但[[半岛电视台|半岛电视台]]表示，南方独立运动拒绝参加会谈，亚丁有数百人发动抗议反对该提议。南方独立运动也宣布撤出联合国调停谈判的权力分享协议，称其“毫无意义<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2015/01/yemen-houthis-hold-boycotted-talks-single-party-150130225551929.html|agency=Al Jazeera|title=Yemen's Houthis hold boycotted talks with single party|date=31 January 2015|accessdate=31 January 2015|archive-date=2020-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200907113336/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2015/01/yemen-houthis-hold-boycotted-talks-single-party-150130225551929.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>”。

到一月底，一些美国媒体报道，美国政府已经开始努力深入到胡塞，努力与该组织建立工作关系，尽管官员有反美立场的观点<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/01/30/world/middleeast/houthis-reach-out-as-they-consolidate-power-in-yemen.html?_r=0|title=Houthis Reach Out as They Cement Power in Yemen|first=Mona|last=Al-Naggar|agency=The New York Times|date=29 January 2015|accessdate=31 January 2015|archive-date=2020-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200505011110/https://www.nytimes.com/2015/01/30/world/middleeast/houthis-reach-out-as-they-consolidate-power-in-yemen.html?_r=0|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.wsj.com/articles/in-strategic-shift-u-s-draws-closer-to-yemeni-rebels-1422576308|agency=Wall Street Journal|title=In Strategic Shift, U.S. Draws Closer to Yemeni Rebels|date=28 January 2015|accessdate=31 January 2015|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108165823/https://www.wsj.com/articles/in-strategic-shift-u-s-draws-closer-to-yemeni-rebels-1422576308|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2月1日，胡塞军“国民大会”召开的前一天，该组织向也门各政治派别发出最后通牒，警告他们如果没有“达成解决当前政治危机的方案”，那么胡塞“革命领导”将担负起国家的正式权力<ref name="houthiultimatum">{{cite news|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2015/02/houthis-set-deadline-resolve-yemen-crisis-150201162733824.html|agency=Al Jazeera|title=Houthis set deadline to resolve Yemen crisis|date=1 February 2015|accessdate=2 February 2015|archive-date=2020-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200907113103/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2015/02/houthis-set-deadline-resolve-yemen-crisis-150201162733824.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.yementimes.com/en/1856/news/4852/Opposition-critical-of-Houthis%E2%80%99-three-day-ultimatum.htm|agency=The Yemen Times|script-title=en:OPPOSITION CRITICAL OF HOUTHIS’ THREE DAY ULTIMATUM|date=2 February 2015|accessdate=2 February 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150326141754/http://www.yementimes.com/en/1856/news/4852/Opposition-critical-of-Houthis%E2%80%99-three-day-ultimatum.htm|archive-date=2015-03-26|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。胡塞军还收购了10架战机和弹药，将其存放在位於[[萨达省|萨达省]]的基地中<ref name="houthiultimatum"/>。

=== 胡塞接管政府 ===
胡塞与也门其他政治派别的谈判过去约一个星期，胡塞武装组织代表在萨那的共和国宫透过电视宣布，到2月6日，组织将正式接管对国家的控制。声明宣布[[也门众议院|众议院]]解散，组建“总统委员会”领导也门两年，“革命委员会”则负责组建由551人组成的新议会<ref name="takeovergovt">{{cite news|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2015/02/06/houthis-yemen-takeover_n_6630070.html|title=Houthi Rebels Take Over Yemen's Government|date=6 February 2015|accessdate=6 February 2015|agency=The Huffington Post|archive-date=2015-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150209013607/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2015/02/06/houthis-yemen-takeover_n_6630070.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Middle-East/2015/Feb-06/286654-yemens-houthi-rebels-announce-they-are-taking-over-the-country-dissolve-parliament.ashx|agency=The Daily Star|title=Yemen's Houthis dissolve parliament, take over power|date=6 February 2015|accessdate=6 February 2015|archive-date=2020-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127001037/https://www.dailystar.com.lb//News/Middle-East/2015/Feb-06/286654-yemens-houthi-rebels-announce-they-are-taking-over-the-country-dissolve-parliament.ashx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。国防部长[[马哈茂德·苏拜希|马哈茂德·苏拜希]]担任最高安全委员会主任<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/02/08/world/middleeast/overture-by-houthis-to-ousted-officials.html|agency=The New York Times|script-title=en:Saudis Unswayed by Houthi Rebels’ Overture in Yemen|date=7 February 2015|accessdate=7 February 2015|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108104440/http://www.nytimes.com/2015/02/08/world/middleeast/overture-by-houthis-to-ousted-officials.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，穆罕默德·阿里·胡塞担任革命委员会负责人，即代总统。联合国拒绝承认声明。反对派联席会议缔约方穆罕默德·萨布里推测，胡塞“政变”会导致也门在国际上被孤立<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2015/02/yemen-houthi-rebels-announce-presidential-council-150206122736448.html|agency=Al Jazeera|title=Yemen's Houthi rebels announce government takeover|date=6 February 2015|accessdate=6 February 2015|archive-date=2019-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190111155622/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2015/02/yemen-houthi-rebels-announce-presidential-council-150206122736448.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[海湾阿拉伯国家合作委员会|海湾阿拉伯国家合作委员会]]谴责政变，美国拒绝声明。2月7日，首都萨那、亚丁、塔伊玆和其他主要城市爆发抗议<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2015/02/thousands-protest-houthi-coup-yemen-150207082035654.html|agency=Al Jazeera|title=Thousands protest against Houthi coup in Yemen|date=7 February 2015|accessdate=7 February 2015|archive-date=2019-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190327123020/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2015/02/thousands-protest-houthi-coup-yemen-150207082035654.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 也门总统哈迪移都亚丁 ===
{{main|也门内战 (2014年至今)}}
2015年2月20日，也门总统哈迪逃离[[胡塞武装组织|胡塞武装组织]]的软禁，从[[萨那|萨那]]前往[[亚丁|亚丁]]<ref>{{cite news|title=也门总统软禁被解除离开首都|url=http://gb.cri.cn/42071/2015/02/22/3245s4879341.htm|accessdate=2015-03-26|newspaper=中国国际广播电台|date=2015-02-21|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304202651/http://gb.cri.cn/42071/2015/02/22/3245s4879341.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=也门总统哈迪离开首都萨那抵达南部城市亚丁|url=http://gb.cri.cn/42071/2015/02/22/3245s4879345.htm|accessdate=2015-03-26|newspaper=中国国际广播电台|date=2015-02-22|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304204731/http://gb.cri.cn/42071/2015/02/22/3245s4879345.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。随后，他收回之前的辞呈<ref>{{cite news|title=“虎口脱险”后，哈迪的路仍漫长|url=http://media.workercn.cn/grrb/2015_02/26/GR0801.htm|accessdate=2015-03-26|newspaper=工人日报|date=2015-02-26|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402094347/http://media.workercn.cn/grrb/2015_02/26/GR0801.htm|archivedate=2015-04-02}}</ref>，海合会国家纷纷将使馆迁至亚丁，以表示对哈迪的支持<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/micro-reading/dzh/2015-03-02/content_13298508.html|title=挺也门总统 巴林迁使馆|newspaper=中国日报网|date=2015-03-02|access-date=2015-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402131500/http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/micro-reading/dzh/2015-03-02/content_13298508.html|archive-date=2015-04-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

